15. UK Regulatory Framework and HSE Alignment 
Health and Safety at Work etc. Act 1974 (HSWA) 
• Duty to ensure safe systems of work 
Management of Health and Safety at Work Regulations 1999 (MHSWR) 
• Requires risk assessment and control measures 
Provision and Use of Work Equipment Regulations 1998 (PUWER) 

• Requires safe isolation of equipment 
Electricity at Work Regulations 1989 
• Requires systems to be made dead and safe 
Pressure Systems Safety Regulations 2000 (PSSR) 
• Controls risks from pressurised systems 
 
HSE Guidance 
• HSG253: Safe Isolation of Plant and Equipment 
• HSG65: Managing for Health and Safety 
 
